# Southwest Greens Ohio — CRM Skill Sheet

## Business Context

Southwest Greens Ohio is Ohio's leading artificial turf and synthetic putting green installer. They serve the entire state (Columbus, Cleveland, Cincinnati, Dayton, Akron, Toledo, Parma) and handle both **residential and commercial** projects.

### Core Service Lines

| Service                 | Key Notes                                                                |
| ----------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------ |
| Golf / Putting Greens   | Flagship product. Outdoor, indoor, basement, Nicklaus Design partnership |
| Artificial Turf & Grass | Residential lawns, commercial applications, Bolt™ Fiber, HydroChill™     |
| Pet & Dog Turf          | Specialized drainage and odor-resistant installations                    |
| Playground Turf         | Schools, parks, retirement communities                                   |
| Sports Turf             | Universities, courts, multi-sport                                        |
| Synthetic Tee Lines     | Golf practice facilities                                                 |

### Business Model

- Leads come in via **quote requests** (web form, phone, walk-in)
- Projects go through a **design → quote → install → follow-up** lifecycle
- Sales team manages relationships; installers handle field work
- Maintenance contracts exist post-installation

