## CRM Data Model

### Lead / Contact Record

```
firstName, lastName, email, phone, address, city, zipCode, ohioRegion
leadSource (web-form | phone | referral | social | walk-in)
projectType (putting-green | artificial-turf | pet-turf | playground | sports-turf | tee-line | other)
projectSubtype (outdoor | indoor | basement | commercial | residential)
squareFootageEstimate
budgetRange
notes
assignedRep
status (new | contacted | consulted | quoted | won | lost | nurturing)
createdAt, updatedAt
```

### Project Record

```
projectId, contactId
serviceType, subtype
locationAddress, city, ohioRegion
squareFootage
productLine (bolt-fiber | hydrochill | nicklaus-design | standard)
estimatedValue, finalValue
installStartDate, installEndDate
installCrew[]
projectStatus (design | quoted | approved | scheduled | in-progress | complete | warranty)
warrantyExpiryDate
attachments[] (photos, contracts, invoices)
notes
```

### Quote Record

```
quoteId, contactId, projectId
lineItems[] { description, qty, unitPrice, total }
totalAmount
validUntil
status (draft | sent | accepted | declined | expired)
sentAt, acceptedAt
```

### Activity / Interaction Log

```
activityId, contactId, projectId?
type (call | email | site-visit | quote-sent | follow-up | install-update | payment)
summary
createdBy (rep)
createdAt
```

### Task Record

```
taskId, contactId?, projectId?
title, description
assignedTo
dueDate
priority (low | medium | high)
status (open | in-progress | done)
```

