## CRM Module Structure

```
/src
  /pages
    /dashboard          ← KPI overview, charts, recent activity
    /leads              ← Lead list, filters, kanban pipeline
    /contacts           ← Contact detail, history, projects
    /projects           ← Project list, timeline, status board
    /quotes             ← Quote builder, send, track
    /tasks              ← Task board / list by rep
    /reports            ← Revenue by service, region, rep
    /settings           ← Users, regions, service config

  /components
    /leads
      LeadCard.tsx
      LeadKanban.tsx
      LeadForm.tsx         ← MUI form inputs
      LeadStatusChip.tsx
