## Project Status Pipeline (Ant Design Stepper Steps)

```
1. Design Consultation
2. Quote Sent
3. Quote Approved
4. Install Scheduled
5. Installation In Progress
6. Project Complete
7. Warranty Active
```

---

## Lead Pipeline Stages (Kanban)

```
New → Contacted → Consulted → Quoted → Won / Lost / Nurturing
```

---

## Key Metrics (Dashboard KPIs)

- Total leads this month / YTD
- Conversion rate (leads → won)
- Revenue closed vs pipeline value
- Average project value by service type
- Leads by Ohio region (map/bar)
- Leads by source (pie chart)
- Open tasks by rep
- Projects in progress (count + value)

